San Francisco is home to several popular tourist attractions that draw visitors from all over the world. One of the most famous attractions is Fisherman's Wharf, located on the northern waterfront. It offers a vibrant and bustling atmosphere with its seafood restaurants, souvenir shops, and street performers. Visitors can also take a boat tour to explore the iconic Alcatraz Island or enjoy stunning views of the Golden Gate Bridge.
